sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sysauto_script"><sysauto_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><business_calendar/><condition/><conditional>false</conditional><entered_time>1970-01-01 00:00:00</entered_time><max_drift/><name>RSS Test</name><offset/><offset_type>0</offset_type><run_as display_value="System Administrator">6816f79cc0a8016401c5a33be04be441</run_as><run_as_tz/><run_dayofmonth>1</run_dayofmonth><run_dayofweek>1</run_dayofweek><run_period/><run_start>2025-10-13 17:55:26</run_start><run_time>1970-01-01 00:00:00</run_time><run_type>on_demand</run_type><script><![CDATA[/**
 * Load AI-related Federal Register documents
 * populate ONLY alert_title + source_url.
 * Run elevated (admin), but no cross-scope writes required.
 */
(function () {
    gs.info('=== Federal Register AI ingest – titles + URLs ===');

    // ----------------------------------------------------
    // 1. Build API request (encoded brackets %5B %5D)
    // ----------------------------------------------------
    var baseUrl = 'https://www.federalregister.gov/api/v1/documents.json';
    var params  = [
        'per_page=100',
        'order=newest',
        'conditions%5Bterm%5D=artificial+intelligence+OR+AI+OR+machine+learning',
        'conditions%5Bpublication_date%5D%5Bgte%5D=2025-01-01',
        'fields%5B%5D=title',          // we only need title…
        'fields%5B%5D=html_url',       // …and html_url for source_url
        'fields%5B%5D=document_number' // used as natural key
    ].join('&');

    var url = baseUrl + '?' + params;

    var req = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2();
    req.setEndpoint(url);
    req.setHttpMethod('get');
    req.setHttpTimeout(15000);

    var res = req.execute();
    if (res.getStatusCode() !== 200) {
        gs.error('Federal Register API failed: ' + res.getStatusCode());
        return;
    }

    var body  = JSON.parse(res.getBody());
    var docs  = body.results || [];
    gs.info('Fetched ' + docs.length + ' documents');

    // ----------------------------------------------------
    // 2. Upsert into Regulatory Alert table
    // ----------------------------------------------------
    var table = 'x_snc_ai_complia_0_regulatory_alert';
    var inserted = 0, updated = 0;

    docs.forEach(function (doc) {
        var number = doc.document_number + ''; // guarantee string
        var gr = new GlideRecord(table);
        gr.addQuery('document_number', number);
        gr.query();

        if (gr.next()) {
            // Already exists – update title / URL if changed
            var changed = false;
            if (gr.alert_title !== doc.title) {
                gr.setValue('alert_title', doc.title);
                changed = true;
            }
            if (gr.source_url !== doc.html_url) {
                gr.setValue('source_url', doc.html_url);
                changed = true;
            }
            if (changed) {
                gr.update();
                updated++;
            }
        } else {
            gr.initialize();
            gr.setValue('document_number', number);
            gr.setValue('alert_title',     doc.title);
            gr.setValue('source_url',      doc.html_url);
            gr.insert();
            inserted++;
        }
    });

    gs.info('Insert/Update complete → new: ' + inserted + ', updated: ' + updated);
})();
]]></script><sys_class_name>sysauto_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2025-10-13 17:55:44</sys_created_on><sys_id>e1b5333d836032107f44c85d50da1ec7</sys_id><sys_mod_count>15</sys_mod_count><sys_name>RSS Test</sys_name><sys_package display_value="AI Compliance Command Center" source="x_snc_ai_complia_0">c203f775836032107f44c85d50da1e64</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="AI Compliance Command Center">c203f775836032107f44c85d50da1e64</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sysauto_script_e1b5333d836032107f44c85d50da1ec7</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2025-10-17 16:54:55</sys_updated_on><time_zone/><upgrade_safe>false</upgrade_safe></sysauto_script></record_update>
